  <resortCombinations><![CDATA[<p>Thanks to a train station near the centre of town, it’s easy to turn your Cinque Terre holiday into a multi-centre. The Renaissance city of <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/city-breaks/florence">Florence</a> is three hours away and, from there, you can explore the stunning Tuscan countryside. Or just head further south to the laid back coastal resort of Viareggio on the <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/tuscany-umbria/tuscany-coast">Tuscany Coast</a>.</p>]]></resortCombinations>
