  <thingsToDo><![CDATA[<p><strong>Hiking</strong></p>
<p>The Cinque Terre is famed for its hiking, with well-trodden paths winding along the coast between the five villages, with fantastic views along the way. We recommend setting out early and catching the train back once you’ve reached the end.</p>]]></thingsToDo>
